/* ==UserStyle==
@name           monospace
@namespace      github.com/openstyles/stylus
@version        2.9.2
@description    My personal changes to codeblocks, etc
@author         Zerohazard8x LLM
@updateURL      https://github.com/Zerohazard8x/custom/raw/main/stylus/monospace.user.styl
@homepageURL    https://github.com/Zerohazard8x/custom/tree/main/stylus
==/UserStyle== */

@-moz-document domain("github.com"), domain("wikipedia.org"), domain("reddit.com"), domain("stackoverflow.com"), domain("superuser.com"), domain("stackexchange.com"), domain("chat.openai.com"), domain("w3schools.com"), domain("tcrf.net"), domain("mariowiki.com"), domain("ssbwiki.com"), domain("wikirby.com"), domain("splatoonwiki.org"), domain("niwanetwork.org"), domain("betawiki.net"), domain("raymanpc.com"), domain("consolemods.org"), domain("wiktionary.org"), domain("bing.com"), domain("copilot.microsoft.com"), domain("geeksforgeeks.org"), domain("discord.com"), domain("duckduckgo.com"), domain("remywiki.com"), domain("cagematch.net"), domain("google.com"), domain("perplexity.ai"), domain("instructure.com"), domain("minecraft.wiki"), domain("pcgamingwiki.com"), domain("liquipedia.net"), domain("redlib.privacyredirect.com"), domain("redlib.catsarch.com") {
    :root {
        /* Define variables */
        --noto: "Noto Sans JP", "Noto Sans TC", "Noto Sans SC", "Noto Sans KR",
            "Noto Sans Thai", "Noto Sans Devanagari", "Noto Sans", PingFang,
            "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", Thonburi,
            "Tiro Devanagari Hindi", "Yu Gothic", "Microsoft YaHei UI",
            "Microsoft YaHei", "Malgun Gothic", "Leelawadee UI", "Nirmala UI";
        /* --noto-full: "Noto Sans JP", "Noto Sans TC", "Noto Sans SC",
            "Noto Sans KR", "Noto Sans Thai", "Noto Sans Devanagari",
            "Noto Sans", "FOT-Rodin Pro", "A-OTF UD Shin Go Pro",
            "FOT-NewRodin Pro", "Hiragino Sans", "Hiragino Sans GB",
            "Hiragino Kaku Gothic", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro", PingFang,
            "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", Thonburi,
            "Tiro Devanagari Hindi", "Yu Gothic", "Microsoft YaHei UI",
            "Microsoft YaHei", "Malgun Gothic", "Leelawadee UI", "Nirmala UI",
            "DFPHSGothic-W5", "DFGHSGothic-W5", "DFHSGothic-W5",
            "DFPGGothicP_U-W5", "DFGGGothicP_U-W5", "DFPHSGothic-W7",
            "DFGHSGothic-W7", "DFHSGothic-W7", "DFPGothic-EB", "DFGGothic-EB",
            "DFGothic-EB", "DFPGothic-SU", "DFGGothic-SU", "DFGothic-SU"; */
        --sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "Roboto",
            var(--noto, "");
        /* --sans-full: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro", "SF Pro Text",
            "Roboto Flex", "Roboto", Barlow, Lato, "Motiva Sans", "Proxima Vara", "Proxima Nova", Inter,
            "Avenir Next", Avenir, "Nunito", "Nunito Sans", "Fira Sans", FiraGO,
            "FF Meta", Manrope, "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica",
            "IBM Plex Sans JP", "IBM Plex Sans KR", "IBM Plex Sans", "Ubuntu",
            var(--noto, ""), "Open Sans", "Droid Sans", ".SF UI Display",
            "SF Pro Display", "SF Compact", "SF Hello"; */
        --serif: "Source Serif Pro", "Source Serif 4", Century,
            "Century Schoolbook", Georgia, "Noto Serif JP", "Noto Serif TC",
            "Noto Serif SC", "Noto Serif KR", "Noto Serif", "Noto Serif Thai",
            var(--noto, "");
        /* --serif-full: "Source Serif", "Source Serif Pro", "Source Serif 4", Fraunces, "Serif UI",
            "Serif UI Text", Alegreya, "Crimson Pro", "Crimson Text",
            Century, "Century Schoolbook", "Century Oldstyle", "Century Old Style", "Garamond Premr Pro", "Libre Baskerville", Georgia, "EB Garamond",
            Lora, "Shippori Mincho", "Serif UI Display", "Noto Serif JP",
            "Noto Serif TC", "Noto Serif SC", "Noto Serif KR", "Noto Serif", var(--noto, ""); */
        --monospace: "Monaspace Argon Var", "Monaspace Argon VF",
            "Monaspace Argon", "Fira Mono";
        /* --monospace-full: "Monaspace Argon Var", "Monaspace Argon VF",
            "Monaspace Argon", "Fira Code VF", "Fira Code", "Fira Mono",
            "Fira Code Retina", "Noto Mono", "Noto Sans Mono", "DroidSansM",
            "SF Mono", "SFMono-Regular", "CodeNewRoman Nerd Font", Consolas,
            Hack, "Hack Nerd Font", "Bitstream Vera Sans Mono",
            "BitstromWera Nerd Font", "DejaVu Sans Mono", "Cascadia Code",
            "CaskaydiaCove Nerd Font", "Cascadia Mono", "Segoe UI Mono",
            "Intel One Mono", Menlo, "MesloLG Nerd Font", Monaco, "Ubuntu Mono",
            "Ubuntu Mono Nerd Font", Agave, "Agave Nerd Font", Hasklig,
            "Hasklug Nerd Font", "Source Code Pro", "Source Code Pro Nerd Font",
            "Andale Mono", "Lucida Console", "Lucida Sans Typewriter"; */
        --block-mono: "JetBrains Mono", "JetBrains Mono NL",
            "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font", "Fantasque Sans Mono";
        /* --block-mono-full: "JetBrains Mono", "JetBrains Mono NL",
            "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font", "Fantasque Sans Mono",
            "FantasqueSansM Nerd Font", "Input Mono", "Envy Code R",
            "EnvyCodeR Nerd Font", "Monaspace Neon Var", "Monaspace Neon VF",
            "Monaspace Neon", "IBM Plex Mono", "BlexMono Nerd Font",
            "Roboto Mono", ProFont, "Monaspace Krypton Var",
            "Monaspace Krypton VF", "Monaspace Krypton", ProFontIIx,
            ProFontWindows, "Iosevka", "Iosevka Nerd Font",
            "IosevkaTerm Nerd Font", "Input Sans"; */
        /* --mono-combo: var(--monospace, ""); */
        --mono-combo: var(--block-mono, ""), var(--monospace, "");
    }
}
